\itemize{
\item \strong{P&L Tracking}: Use \code{price}, \code{size}, \code{fee}, and \code{fee_currency} for profit calculations.
\item \strong{Fill Analysis}: Check \code{liquidity} (maker/taker) to optimise execution strategy.
\item \strong{Audit Trail}: Build comprehensive trade logs with \code{trade_id} for reconciliation.
}
}

