\subsection{Method \code{cancel_order_by_id_sync()}}{
Cancel Order by Order ID (Synchronous Return)

Cancels an order and waits for the cancellation to complete before returning.
Returns the final order state including fill and cancellation sizes.
\subsection{API Endpoint}{

\verb{DELETE https://api.kucoin.com/api/v1/hf/orders/sync/\{orderId\}?symbol=\{symbol\}}
}

\subsection{Official Documentation}{

\href{https://www.kucoin.com/docs-new/rest/spot-trading/orders/cancel-order-by-orderld-sync}{KuCoin Cancel Order By OrderId Sync}

Verified: 2026-05-23
}

\subsection{Automated Trading Usage}{
\itemize{
\item \strong{Atomic Cancel}: Confirm cancellation and get final fill state in one call.
\item \strong{Partial Fill Detection}: Check \code{deal_size} to know if any fills occurred before cancellation.
}
}

